To use the native notification system OSX requires packages to be signed and compiled using their platform and tools. This is not very friendly for Node users so we are using the tiny signed native application [Terminal Notifer](https://github.com/alloy/terminal-notifier) from [Eloy DurÃ¡n](https://github.com/alloy). We're stuck with the default icon for now, if anybody knows how it would be nice if we could use the Grunt logo or something custom instead.

